<% content_for :page_title, "Privacy Policy" %>

<section class="bg-white w-full">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 lg:px-20 lg:py-20">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-campaign-gold h-7 w-[3px]"></div>
      <span class="text-campaign-gold font-sans text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase">Legal</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 font-sans text-sm mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none font-sans text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you interact with the Clough for SC5 campaign website, we may collect the following information:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Volunteer Signups:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, zip code, and any message or interests you provide.</li>
        <li><strong>Contact Forms:</strong> Information you voluntarily submit through contact or inquiry forms.</li>
        <li><strong>Automated Data:</strong> Basic analytics data including pages visited, referral source, browser type, and general location (city-level). This data is anonymized and used solely to improve our website.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Coordinate volunteer activities and campaign outreach</li>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
        <li>Send campaign updates and event notifications (only if you opt in)</li>
        <li>Improve our website and campaign communications</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for their marketing purposes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Donations</h2>
      <p>All donations are processed through <a href="https://secure.actblue.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-campaign-gold hover:underline">ActBlue</a>, a third-party donation platform. When you donate, you are subject to ActBlue's own privacy policy and terms of service. We do not collect or store your credit card or financial information. ActBlue provides us with donor names, addresses, and contribution amounts as required by the Federal Election Commission (FEC).</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
      <p>Our website uses cookies and similar technologies for basic analytics purposes, including understanding which pages are visited and how users navigate the site. This data is aggregated and anonymized. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>ActBlue</strong> — donation processing</li>
        <li><strong>Social Media Platforms</strong> — Facebook, X (Twitter), Instagram (linked from our site)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These services have their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review them.</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Choices</h2>
      <p>You may:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Opt out of campaign communications at any time by contacting us</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal data by contacting us</li>
        <li>Control cookies through your browser settings</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our website is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or wish to exercise your data rights, contact us at:</p>
      <p><strong>Clough for SC5</strong><br>
      Email: <a href="mailto:info@cloughforsc5.com" class="text-campaign-gold hover:underline">info@cloughforsc5.com</a></p>

      <h2 class="text-navy-900 font-display text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">11. FEC Disclosure</h2>
      <p>Contributions to Clough for SC5 are not tax-deductible. Federal law requires us to use our best efforts to collect and report the name, mailing address, occupation, and employer of individuals whose contributions exceed $200 in an election cycle.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
